    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Benefits of Using Durable Milk Crates</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Investing in high-quality milk crates offers several tangible benefits for Canadian dairy distributors:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-10">
      <li><span class="font-semibold">Cost Savings</span>: Durable crates reduce the frequency of replacements, lowering long-term expenses.</li>
      <li><span class="font-semibold">Product Protection</span>: Strong crates prevent tipping and breakage, minimizing product loss and spoilage.</li>
      <li><span class="font-semibold">Operational Efficiency</span>: Standardized, stackable crates make handling faster and safer.</li>
