    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Selecting the Right Milk Crate for Your Operations</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-10">
      <li><span class="font-semibold">Volume and Size</span>: Match crate size to bottle type and quantity. For example, 6-cell crates are ideal for half-gallon glass bottles, while 12-cell crates suit quart-sized containers.</li>
      <li><span class="font-semibold">Material Durability</span>: High-quality plastic withstands repeated handling, transport, and stacking.</li>
      <li><span class="font-semibold">Stacking and Storage</span>: Ensure crates are compatible with storage racks, delivery trucks, and warehouse setups.</li>
      <li><span class="font-semibold">Color Coding and Organization</span>: Different colors can help streamline inventory management, reduce errors, and speed up distribution processes.</li>
      <li><span class="font-semibold">Reusability and Maintenance</span>: Crates should be easy to clean and maintain for multiple uses over time.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Operational Tips for Dairy Distributors</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">To maximize the benefits of milk crates, distributors can adopt best practices:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-10">
      <li><span class="font-semibold">Implement a Crate Tracking System</span>: Keep track of crate location and usage to reduce loss and misplacement.</li>
      <li><span class="font-semibold">Train Staff on Handling Procedures</span>: Proper lifting, stacking, and loading techniques prevent accidents and product damage.</li>
      <li><span class="font-semibold">Regular Maintenance</span>: Inspect crates for cracks, wear, or other damage to maintain safety and durability.</li>
      <li><span class="font-semibold">Plan Logistics Around Crate Efficiency</span>: Use stackable crates to optimize space in trucks and storage areas, reducing delivery costs.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Sustainability and Environmental Impact</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Reusable milk crates significantly contribute to sustainable operations. By reducing the need for single-use containers, dairy distributors can:</p>
