    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-10">Many consumers are increasingly attentive to sustainable packaging practices. Distributors who adopt reusable milk crates not only save costs but also demonstrate their commitment to sustainability, which can differentiate them in competitive markets.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Trends in Dairy Packaging and Distribution</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Canadian dairy distribution is evolving with several key trends:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-10">
      <li><span class="font-semibold">Automation-Friendly Crates</span>: Crates compatible with automated handling and packing systems improve efficiency in high-volume operations.</li>
      <li><span class="font-semibold">Smart Packaging Integration</span>: Incorporating QR codes or RFID tags in crates can help track product location and monitor temperature or handling conditions.</li>
