    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Real-World Example: Color-Coded Distribution</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-10">A dairy distributor in Ontario implemented color-coded crates: green for milk, blue for cream, and red for specialty products. This simple system reduced loading errors, improved speed in warehouses, and minimized product mix-ups. Combined with durable Pacific Injection Molding crates, the distributor experienced a significant increase in operational efficiency and customer satisfaction.</p>

